CREATE TABLE `UserRecord` (
  `id` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_contacts` varchar(255)  NOT NULL,
  `message` longtext  NOT NULL,
  `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT '0000-00-00 00:00:00',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
)


I have created table by using migration feature of laravel by create_user_table that is in dataBase folder of laravel.
but for your use  i have given this query which will create the same table structure. 